data.description: Fabulous move-in-ready home with great privacy on a large lot only seven minutes from I-540 (opening 2024). Set on a beautiful acre lot, this home lives like a ranch & features a huge bonus room & full bath upstairs.  Both HVAC units & roof replaced in last 5 years. New engineered wood floors in living areas.  Kitchen features appliances replaced in 2021 & lots of counter space.  Oversized primary bedroom suite w/ large soaking tub & walk-in shower.  Walk-in closet features a hidden 3x3 safe room.  Large covered porch, attached deck, lower deck & fire pit are great for entertaining.  Second floor finished & permitted in 2018 provides incredible space & opportunities.  Lots of unheated storage off bonus room w/ built-in shelving.  Oversized two car garage provides room for a workbench & storage.  Large shed in great condition.  Play structure in side yard does not convey.  Decks & front porch railings freshly painted.  New carpet on stairs.  Gutter guards just installed.  11 minutes to Costco, 13 minutes to Fuquay-Varina & 23 minutes to Downtown Raleigh.  Country living but convenient to everything! No city taxes!
